name: My Sweet Prince
wikiSummary: "My Sweet Prince" is a song by British rock group Placebo from their album "Without You I'm Nothing". It was featured in the soundtrack on the second series of Trigger Happy TV. The song has a quiet and sad mood with quiet piano and soothing vocals. The song is about heroin.
wikiText:
"My Sweet Prince" is a song by British rock group Placebo from their album "Without You I'm Nothing". It was featured in the soundtrack on the second series of Trigger Happy TV. The song has a quiet and sad mood with quiet piano and soothing vocals. The song is about heroin.
